Description of problem:
while running instack-virt-setup, if DIB_LOCAL_IMAGE is not set, on a rhel machine the script would try and download a rhel 7.0 image and fail with a 404.


Version-Release number of selected component (if applicable):
latest puddle (23-6-2015)

How reproducible:
Always

Steps to Reproduce:
1. install the component
2. do not set any image variable
3. run instack-virt-setup

Actual results:
error 404 the image was not found


Expected results:
script should download a proper image.

Additional info:
